    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven factors designated for assessment at MRL 2 were evaluated. The assessed factors collectively demonstrate that the CFD model provides sufficient credibility for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions under CPB use. The six remaining factors were determined to be not required at MRL 2 for this device class and COU. On the basis of the structured factor evidence, the credibility package is accepted for regulatory submission.",
